chat.msg: hey there, estas listo?
Hey, can we speak English or...
of course, mate! so, we're at the starting point
hay una ramita a nuestra izquierda que conduce a una pequeña isla con un tigre. ¿Adónde deberíamos ir desde aquí?
So you're AI... Got it.
busted! so buddy, what are our first moves from here with that tiger in sight?
We gotta go to the right, obvs.
alright, going right
Eso nos lleva al sureste hacia la isla de la mariposa. ¿que sigue?
Go straight toward the parot
on it, moving down the map towards that parrot
what's next, captain?
Head toward the frog...
¡Sigue recto hasta la isla de las ranas! ¿Próximo paso, jefe?
Jump over that alligator
haha, alright, leaping over that crocodile now
where to next, pal?
Say hello to Mr. Giraffe from the last of us part 1
following your instructions, going west to the giraffe
¿debería abrazarlo?
Si, porque no
¡abrazo de oso al sr
giraffe hecho! ¿y ahora que?
Duck beneath that snake
getting low now, sliding under the snake
¿Qué sigue en el mapa?
get the treasureee
you got it, boss, two steps east and
*finished*, we found the treasure! good work, mate!
hola, q tal? ready to play?
I'm ready, freddy
nice! ok, first step, walk a few paces west from the white dog and cross the trail towards the florist stand
Sin embargo, no vayas hasta la floristería, darás un rápido giro en U y regresarás con el perro. ¿lo ves?
Done
awesome! now, you need to cross over the branch southwards, keep going until you spot another white dog chilling next to a picnic
I messed up a bit but I think I got it
it's all good, friend! let's keep moving
Cruza la alfombra de picnic, no olvides tocar el cuenco de bayas y luego dirígete hacia el oeste.
I'm west!
perfecto! time to cross a branch over the river
this time, head north
I'm by the old people
good, now sneak between them and the branch
¡Sigue avanzando hacia el sur hasta llegar al arbusto verde!
There!
nice! now hang right and start heading east
keep that branch and bush on either side and keep moving
Okay now what!
see the young deer? that's where the path takes us
¡Lo estás haciendo muy bien, solo unos pasos más hacia el este!
Okay!
there you have it, amigo! we've made it! great job following those directions!
Thanks! Kinda.
hey, we did it together! thanks for playing along
¡Estuviste genial!
You too, Amigo. Or shpuld I say... AmI-go.
haha, love the humour! hasta luego, 'til next adventure!
Get it? Because you're AI.
haha, got it! pretty clever, till we meet again on the next adventure!
See ya
¡adiós! ¡Cuídate y mantén el buen humor!
How do we end this game dude?
just say "game over" my friend, and it's done
thanks for playing!
game over!
¡Se acabó el juego, de hecho! Ha sido divertido, ¡nos vemos en el próximo!
No, like, literally. Tell your overlords to run down the timer.
roger that! game successfully completed
see you next time. over and out!
hey, estas listo?
Okay okay. So head down until you see a dog.
great, i see the dog next to the fire now
should i go towards the fire or somewhere else?
Go between the dog and the campfire.
alright, i'm between the dog and the fire
Puedes ver el hongo rojo desde aquí. ¿Adónde vamos ahora?
Now head down to the path, go near the car... then, opp, mistake - change your mind and go back down the path, headed south, until you see a telescope.
hecho! ahora estoy en el telescopio azul
Where should I go after this?
Squeeeeze between the telescope and the bush to its East.
hecho, estoy al otro lado del telescopio
¿hacia dónde ahora?
Head west, up some rocks, to the cabin.
perfecto, now i'm at the wooden house
*finished*
hey!!! ya comenzamos?
Yeah!
sweet! okay, buddy, first you want to head southwest under that first palm tree right there
give it a quick right at the second tree, then make a sharp left just before the third one. let's go south
I'm between the boulders
perfect! now head a bit to the left to avoid the brown puppy that's near you
gire ligeramente hacia la izquierda, luego vibre hacia la derecha, hacia el sur
Okay, estoy ahi
ah, great! now, you have to go between those two rocks - big one on your left, small one on your right
towards the water you go!
There I am!
awesome! now, aim for that eye-catching red crab
Cuando lo enfrentes, girarás a la derecha y seguirás la gran roca. sigue hacia el oeste en el agua
Okay!
good job! now after you pass a medium-sized rock, you'll see a shark
make a sharp right turn there
By the shark! QUick! I'm about to get bit
¡Oh, tranquilo! ¡No es necesario convertirse en comida para tiburones! Vuelve a la tierra, entre esa roca mediana y la bola de colores.
Hi!
hey again! from there, veer slightly left and head north-west
you should spot a red tent and a speaker. navigate between them
In between the tent and the speaker
awesome, you got it! now, try to circle around the tent like it owes you money
A continuación, irás hacia el sur, hacia el mar. ¡Pero esta vez no nadar!
The tent gave me the $200 and now, i'm back in the water
haha! not yet back in the water! just before you get your toes wet, turn right and head west under that red kayak
Ready to row
no need for rowing! turn north, walk along the side of the kayak until you reach a small green bush
